description: Naruto and Minato combine their powers to perform a Sage Jutsu attack on Obito. Obito decides to speed up his plan to perform the Infinite Tsukuyomi and summons the Divine Tree.
title: The Divine Tree

description: The barrier is shattered, and Ten Tails appears! With unfathomable power in its attack, it sends shock waves through the air.
title: The Allied Shinobi Forces Jutsu

description: Shikaku outlines his final strategy, in which Nine Tails will send its chakra to increase everyone's strength. United in their cause, Naruto and the Allied Shinobi set out to take on Ten Tails.

input: Those Who Dance in the Shadows

title: Those Who Dance in the Shadows

description: As the fighting rages on between the Senju and Uchiha, Hashirama approaches Madara about an alliance. But Madara refuses to listen and releases Susano'o instead!
title: Era of Warring States

description: As children in a strife-filled time, Hashirama meets Madara Uchiha and the two talk about their hopes for the future.
title: Hashirama and Madara

description: Ten Tails' relentless attack is wearing down Naruto, and his chakra begins to dissipate. Meanwhile, Kakashi and Obito face each other in a different Kamui dimension.
title: Hole

description: Ten Tails is on the brink of its final transformation and begins to form a massive Tailed Beast Bomb.
title: Something to Fill the Hole

description: Standing on the cliff where they first confided their hopes to each other, Hashirama and Madara gaze at their burgeoning village.
title: My True Dream

description: After listening to what Hashirama and the rest of the former Hokage have to say, Sasuke decides on the path he will ultimately take.
title: Sasuke's Answer

description: Sakura focuses on her healing skills while Naruto and Sasuke aim for Ten Tails. Meanwhile, the five Kage battling Madara have sustained critical injuries.
title: The New Three-Way Deadlock

description: Kakashi holds on to the hope that Obito can return to being the young man that he remembers. But Obito has abandoned the present as well as the memories of his friends and will not try to stop the Infinite Tsukuyomi.
title: Kakashi vs. Obito

description: Part 2 of a special two-part extra edition!  Lee and company rush over and encounter a strange man who is so strong that even Neji can't defeat him.
title: Naruto vs. Mecha Naruto

description: Obito completely absorbs the giant Ten Tails, undergoes a transformation and becomes the Ten Tails' Jinchuriki.
title: The Ten Tails' Jinchuriki

description: Hashirama and Madara continue their old grudge match and fiercely battle while the other shinobi are unable to do anything but watch helplessly from the sidelines.
title: An Opening

description: The Allied Forces receive a report that Omoi has deserted his post, much to the Raikage's shock.
title: Run, Omoi!

description: Hashirama, Tobirama, Hiruzen, the Five Kage, Orochimaru and every shinobi on the battlefield join together to cut down the Divine Tree!
title: Pursuing Hope

description: Naruto and Killer Bee face off against the masked man originally thought to be Madara Uchiha.

input: The Unbreakable Mask and the Shattered Bubble
Unbreakable Mask and the Shattered Bubble

title: The Unbreakable Mask and the Shattered Bubble

description: Naruto and Killer Bee take on the six Reanimated Jinchuriki, who've been equipped with the Rinnegan.
title: Jinchuriki vs. Jinchuriki!!

description: Kakashi and Guy arrive in the nick of time to back up Naruto and Killer Bee. The fight intensifies even further when three out of the six Reanimated Jinchuriki enter Tailed Beast State.

input: Four Tails, the King of Sage Monkeys
Tails, the King of Sage Monkeys

title: Four Tails, the King of Sage Monkeys

description: As Naruto continues to try and free Four Tails from Madara's control, Nine Tails begins to undergo a surprising change.
title: Kurama

description: The tide of battle is slowly shifting in the Allied Forces' favor, but many are uncertain that they really stand a chance against Madara Uchiha.
title: Promise of Victory

description: Naruto uses up the last of his chakra trying to free the Tailed Beasts from Madara's control.
title: Two-Man Team

description: Just when the Third Tsuchikage is about to give up, he remembers the words of the previous Tsuchikage. Realizing their true meaning, he regains the will to fight.
title: A Will of Stone

description: Kabuto attempts to bring Sasuke over to his side by pointing out that they both are fighting for the same goal: to bring down the Leaf Village.
title: To Each Their Own Leaf

description: Sasuke and Itachi team up to stop Kabuto's Reanimation Jutsu.
title: Sibling Tag Team

description: Itachi declares that Kabuto's actions will not lead to what he truly desires and prepares the Uchiha's Ultimate Visual Jutsu that determines an adversary's fate!
title: The Izanami Activated

description: Kabuto's past is finally revealed.
title: Kabuto Yakushi

description: Itachi activates the Visual Jutsu Izanami to trap Kabuto's mind.
title: Izanagi and Izanami

description: Thanks to Itachi, the Reanimation Jutsu is released, and all the Reanimated Shinobi are returned to their resting places. But to everyone's surprise, the real Madara still remains!
title: Reanimation Jutsu, Release!

description: The Five Kage watch helplessly as Madara activates his Perfect Susano'o to destroy them.
title: I Will Love You Always

description: Kakashi is disturbed to discover a strange connection between the masked man's Transportation Technique and his own Kamui Jutsu.
title: Who Are You?

description: Naruto and the others are further shocked when they learn that Obito has been working with Madara Uchiha for years to orchestrate Project Tsuki no Me.
title: Obito and Madara

description: Obito works to rehabilitate his injured body in the hopes of being reunited with Kakashi and Rin.
title: I'm in Hell

description: Obito decides to carry out Madara's dream so that he can create an ideal world where Rin still exists.
title: World of Dreams

description: Kakashi becomes part of the ANBU Black Ops, an elite team of shinobi who are under the direct command of the Fourth Hokage, Minato Namikaze.

title: Kakashi: Shadow of the ANBU Black Ops - Coup d'État

description: Working in sync, Naruto and Sasuke prepare to attack in the same way Madara once did, cloaking Kurama in Susano'o's robes.
title: A Heart Filled With Comrades

description: Obito's turned every shinobi against him and intends on ending the world. Naruto then asserts that Obito is merely abandoning everything and running away.
title: Obito Uchiha

description: Naruto's power of persuasion moves Obito's heart. Due to the influence of the Ten Tails, visions of himself and Rin from the past appear in the inner realm and play havoc with Obito's emotions.
title: The Promise That Was Kept

description: Naruto and the Allied Shinobi Forces successfully extract the Tailed Beasts from Obito. Only Madara remains, and Naruto heads out to tackle this foe.
title: Madara Uchiha Rises

description: The Tailed Beasts and the Allied Shinobi Forces shift their focus onto their greatest foe, Madara Uchiha.
title: My First Friend

description: Hanabi adores her sister Hinata, who struggles to become a worthy successor to the Hyuga Clan.
title: The Adored Elder Sister

description: When Hinata is labeled unfit as a successor, Hanabi's heart becomes bound to her destiny.
title: Hanabi's Decision

description: Naruto loses Kurama during his battle against Madara and is near death. As Tsunade and the other Leaf Village shinobi watch in fear, they are reminded that Naruto has always been their symbol of hope, even when he was not with them…
title: The New Chunin Exams

description: Despite all efforts, Kurama is extracted from Naruto, and ultimately, all the Tailed Beasts are imprisoned inside the Gedo Statue.
title: A True Ending

description: The Hidden Leaf begin preparing for the Chunin Exams. Tsunade orders Kakashi to personally deliver an invitation to the Hidden Rain Village and, at the same time, gather intel.
title: The Chunin Exams Begin!

description: The Chunin Exams finally begin and the proctor for Round One is none other than Shikamaru!
title: The Three Questions

description: Shikamaru introduces another question to be answered within three minutes. Will Neji and his team be able to pass this round?
title: One Worthy as a Leader

description: Kankuro tries in vain to stop Gaara from supervising the exams due to the lack of security and the threats against his life.

input: The Night Before the Second Exam

title: The Night Before the Second Exam

description: The Second Exam finally begins! To pass this stage, each team must take possession of both the Heaven and Earth scrolls and make it to the designated site in the center of the Demon Desert within 72 hours.
title: Demon Desert Survival

description: Like Lee, Shira can only use taijutsu. Gaara recognizes Shira's taijutsu abilities and appoints him as personal taijutsu coach.
title: As a Taijutsu User

description: Lee challenges Shira to a battle between taijutsu users!  Lee is pushed into using his Eight Inner Gates, but he is unable to release the First Gate!
title: The Ultimate

description: Kiba, Hinata and Shino head out into the desert, and three Hidden Grass Shinobi appear before them!
title: Escape vs. Pursuit

description: As fighting breaks out for the scrolls, Tenten feels an intense rivalry with Ajisai, who also specializes in Transportation Ninjutsu.
title: Tenten's Troubles

description: Kiba and his team are in pursuit of Hidden Grass Ninja who have stolen their scroll.
title: Unwavering Gutsiness

description: Witnessing Ajisai's proficiency with the Summoning Jutsu, Tenten recalls her training with Guy.
title: The Imprisoned Pair

description: Ino, Sakura and Choji trudge across the desert without any provisions. Ino and Sakura start arguing when a giant scorpion attacks.
title: The Place Where I Belong

description: As Ino and her team head toward an oasis, they are attacked by a team of Sand Shinobi comprised of Ameno, Shishio, and Kouji.
title: The Yamanaka Clan: Secret Ninjutsu

description: Sakura and her team continue their trek across the desert towards the goal. When they stop to rest, they encounter a puppet manipulated by a rival team from the Sand.
title: The Cursed Puppet

description: Sakura realizes that she has trained with Lady Tsunade and regains her confidence that she can protect Ino and Choji from the Sand Shinobi.
title: Their Backs

description: The Sand Jonin Fugi sneaks into the Demon Desert and creates a massive sandstorm in order to assassinate Gaara, the Fifth Kazekage.

input: The Hidden Plot Set Into Motion

title: The Hidden Plot Set Into Motion
